{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"240554e452","title":"复彭德怀电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c812d4876c","index":0,"year":1949,"month":8,"day":26,"articleId":"240554e452"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"77dd4e68a1","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"240554e452","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东复彭德怀电的主要内容。"},{"id":"2bbaf5a16c","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"240554e452","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭德怀25日24时电告：攻城部队25日拥晓对兰州守敌发起攻击，与故恶战一天，故我伤亡相等。马鸿迷部4个军8万人左右，正倾巢援兰州，似有放弃宁夏模样，如能经过傅作义退延宁马10日或半月出动，对我有利。根据上述情形，我军拟留六十二军停临夏，一、二两军东移，参加攻击兰州之敌及便于适时打击增援兰州的宁夏马鸿速部。"}],"contents":[{"id":"509024ac83","type":"title","text":"复彭德怀电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"240554e452"},{"id":"77dd4e68a1","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）完全同意二十五日二十四时电的部署。（二）六十二军暂留临夏，必要时亦宜令其移兰州参战。（三）务请注意筹足至少一个月的粮食、弹药，准备持久坚决歼灭两马。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"240554e452"}],"page":{"id":"b8ce19fd91","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"240554e452","start":179,"end":179}}}},"__N_SSG":true}